09:14.780 --> 09:25.780
illustration. after going through it that second time i'll sit down and start to
develop thumbnail sketches which are just a small drawings um on scrap paper

09:25.780 --> 09:35.980
actually and try to formulate an idea of what i i would like to illustrate from
