12:02.280 --> 12:10.160
someone who's been in the field as long as he has. And to have an author tell me
that I've captured a particular character or scene exactly the way they had it

12:10.160 --> 12:20.160
in mind is probably, for me, the highest praise that an illustrator can get. And
